<br />

<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;ClearBits &#40;pev-&gt;flags, FL_MONSTER&#41;;
<br />

<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;SetThink&#40;MySentryDeath&#41;; // Change think funtion so I don't try to shoot etc.
<br />

